00:36:56,590 --> 00:36:59,091
Well, he did mention something
about calling the police.

540
00:36:59,175 --> 00:37:01,677
Oh, the police. The police?

541
00:37:01,761 --> 00:37:05,431
Oh . That I cannot have. I'd better
