559
00:40:02,942 --> 00:40:04,651
I just can't seem to.

560
00:40:05,111 --> 00:40:07,279
He makes me write down
everything in there.

561
00:40:07,363 --> 00:40:09,323
What I get, what I spend.

562
00:40:10,283 --> 00:40:13,869
I used to have a checking account,
